1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,080
Let's see how much you know: 10 questions will stand in your way.

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:09,560
A question and 6 possible answers will appear on screen.

3
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:13,480
Choose the correct one together and remember its number.

4
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:17,680
At each terminal, you will see six numbers, each in a different color.

5
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:21,520
Find the correct number and press its color.

6
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:24,920
When all of you answer, you will see the result.

7
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:28,240
A single mistake will break your streak.

8
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:30,960
Think fast, think as one.
